21/03/2007
PRISTINA, Kosovo, Serbia -- The two biggest political parties in Kosovo, the Democratic League of Kosovo and the Democratic Party of Kosovo, announced on Tuesday (March 20th) that they decided to form a coalition in the Gjilan municipality.
Party officials hope the local-level partnership might lead to a coalition at the national level.
(ANA-MPA, ERT, Tanjug, Darik, RTK, KosovaLive - 20/03/07)
